sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Settings UI
    participant REST as REST PUT /api/settings/physics
    participant OSA as OptimizedSettingsActor
    participant Neo4j as Neo4j Persistence
    participant FCA as ForceComputeActor (GPU)
    participant GSS as GraphServiceSupervisor
    participant POA as PhysicsOrchestratorActor
    participant GSA as GraphStateActor
    participant CCA as ClientCoordinatorActor

    UI->>REST: PUT physics JSON patch
    REST->>OSA: GetSettings
    OSA-->>REST: AppFullSettings snapshot
    REST->>REST: Merge patch, validate
    REST->>OSA: UpdateSettings{merged}
    OSA-->>REST: Ok

    Note over REST: Propagate to GPU actors

    REST->>FCA: UpdateSimulationParams (direct via AppState)
    FCA->>FCA: Update sim_params, reset warmup

    REST->>GSS: UpdateSimulationParams
    GSS->>POA: Forward UpdateSimulationParams
    POA->>POA: Update target_params + simulation_params
    POA->>POA: Reset fast-settle state if changed
    POA->>FCA: do_send(UpdateSimulationParams) (redundant fallback)

    REST-->>Neo4j: Persist physics JSON (async)

    Note over POA,GSA: BROKEN PATH: Physics stays paused
    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
        Note over POA: If physics was paused from equilibrium,<br/>is_physics_paused = false (line 1354)
        Note over POA: BUT: schedule_next_pipeline_step<br/>only fires if simulation_running == true<br/>AND gpu_initialized == true
        Note over POA: If simulation was stopped by<br/>equilibrium auto-pause, simulation_running<br/>may be false -- pipeline never restarts
    end

    rect rgb(255, 200, 200)
        Note over GSA: GraphStateActor PhysicsState<br/>is NEVER updated -- no message sent
        Note over CCA: No ForcePositionBroadcast sent<br/>Clients see stale positions
    end

    rect rgb(255, 200, 200)
        Note over REST: NO ForceResumePhysics sent<br/>from settings route to POA
        Note over POA: Orchestrator relies on internal<br/>unpause logic which may not trigger<br/>if simulation_running is already false
    end
